    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Demo</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The demo includes the first 2 levels and takes about 25 minutes to complete.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discord channel</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267660/extras/94cb810200f3da0d70c817dc87a7bd11.avif?t=1758214296\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267660/extras_big/94cb810200f3da0d70c817dc87a7bd11.avif?t=1758214296 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLOT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Backrooms: Rescue Expedition</i> is a <u>new</u> game about liminal spaces. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267660/extras/5c7c1155b2226abcb6e4a228bf9002f5.avif?t=1758214296\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267660/extras_big/5c7c1155b2226abcb6e4a228bf9002f5.avif?t=1758214296 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a group of 4 people armed with modernized HAZMAT suits. The leader of the group has the equipment to open the doors on level 15 Futuristic Halls . Bringing the equipment and <strong>rescuing the lost research group is your main task</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RESCUE THE GROUP: SOLO OR COOP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267660/extras/6938df58f9cf9b358ce321e592e3ebe1.avif?t=1758214296\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267660/extras_big/6938df58f9cf9b358ce321e592e3ebe1.avif?t=1758214296 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can go to the back rooms alone, or you can go through them in a team of 2, 3 or 4 players. Co-op is never forced when it comes to mandatory objectives, but working together can be very rewarding. Regardless of the number of players on your team, the key is to survive and escape the liminal spaces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
